    <item>
      <title>Best High-Capacity Portable Power Stations for Van Life</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/high-capacity-power-stations/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/high-capacity-power-stations/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;High-capacity portable stations are for van setups that have moved past occasional charging and into daily, sustained energy use. If your workflow includes long laptop blocks, Starlink time, or electric cooking bursts, this is the tier where power stops feeling tight.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Best Budget Build Tools for a First Van Conversion</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/budget-build-tools/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/budget-build-tools/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;You do not need a garage full of tools for a strong first build. You need a small set of reliable tools and a clear sequence.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;callout-shortcode&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p class=&#34;callout-title&#34;&gt;Quick Answer&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;callout-body&#34;&gt;Buy fewer tools but buy reliable core tools: drill/driver, jigsaw, rivnut tool, crimper, torque wrench, and safety gear.&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We’re keeping this high-level—no wiring instructions here. For installs, follow manufacturer guidance or work with a qualified installer.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Best Budget Solar for Van Life</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-solar/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-solar/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want the quick answer: most budget builders should start with a &lt;strong&gt;200W to 400W system&lt;/strong&gt; paired with a battery bank sized for one day of normal use. Oversizing too early is one of the fastest ways to blow a build budget.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Best Budget Van Kitchen Gear</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-kitchen/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/best-of/van-kitchen/</guid>
