cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;Signal Booster Kit&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Weak-signal zones&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$$$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Better call/data stability&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Can amplify weak/noisy signal&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3 font-semibold&#34;&gt;Phone Tether Backup Setup&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Tight budgets&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;$&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Lowest-cost backup strategy&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;Inconsistent under heavy work use&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;td class=&#34;border-b p-3&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow-sm border border-neutral-300 bg-transparent text-neutral-500 opacity-70 cursor-not-allowed&#34; aria-disabled=&#34;true&#34;&gt;Link coming soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;space-y-3 md:hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;article class=&#34;rounded-lg border p-4&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-base font-semibold&#34;&gt;Van Hotspot Router Setup&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;mt-2 text-sm&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Best For:&lt;/strong&gt; Full-time remote work&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
